    <h2 class="reveal d1">You were made<br/>to be <em>loved like this.</em></h2>
    <p class="reveal d2">Start your 24 days with Jesus. Let His love meet you exactly where you are.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="cta-btns reveal d2">
